onsible for the life''s of innocent?\n\nMay God give strength to their family!!!! RIP INNOCENT SOULS.............\n\nhERE HOW CM Akhilesh Yadav tweeted with the list of helpline numbers-\n\n[caption id="attachment_181" align="alignnone" width="872"]<a href="http://www.maikalaal.com/shocking-tragedy-kanpur-patna-express-death-tolls-increases-96-150-injured/capture121/" rel="attachment wp-att-181"><img class="wp-image-181" src="http://www.maikalaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Capture121-300x174.png" alt="Northern Railway helpline" width="872" height="506" /></a> Northern Railway helpline[/caption]\n\n# All the Howrah, Mumbai rail routes have been disrupted due to such a grief-stricken incident.\n\nPM Modi has announced with his sorrowful soul- 2 lakhs to family of dead &amp; 50,000 to family of injured people in the shocking incident.\n\n[caption id="attachment_185" align="alignnone" width="482"]<a href="http://www.maikalaal.com/shocking-tragedy-kanpur-patna-express-death-tolls-increases-96-150-injured/narendra-modi_650x400_81479022071/" rel="attachment wp-att-185"><img class=" wp-image-185" src="http://www.maikalaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/narendra-modi_650x400_81479022071-300x185.jpg" alt="Narendra Modi" width="482" height="297" /></a> Narendra Modi[/caption]\n\nAll the local village people are working hand in hand with the railway employees to save as much life they can. Many people are fighting back with injuries and they are getting transferred to the government hospitals for treatment, so that lives their life''s can be saved with NO loss of life.\n\nSuresh Prabhu, will be reaching the incident place soon to monitor all the operations effectively and will try to know the loopholes which resulted in such a disastrous situation which has costed many precious life.\n\nSo, pray to all your almighty so that the worsening tragedy gets recovered soon.\n\nEvery year I noticed this type of Train crashes, which costs 100 of lives, it''s clear now that we have a lot of shortfalls in our Indian Railway System.\n\nHow to stop these tragedies from happening next time?\n\nThis is influential concern.....May be soon we will know the drawbacks due to which this crash occurred. Only middle class &amp; poor class suffers the most because maximum of our exploding population come under middle range of per capital income and others with low per capital who travel the most in trains nowadays.', 'Shocking tragedy in Kanpur- Patna Express , death tolls increases to 96 more than 150 injured', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '176-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-11-20 13:15:01', '2016-11-20 13:15:01', '', 176, 'http://www.maikalaal.com/176-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
